<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Zorin Mobile Shop</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 60px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            padding: 60px 40px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        .header p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            opacity: 0.95;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 60px 40px;
        }

        .section {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .section:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #667eea;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .section-title::before {
            content: '';
            width: 4px;
            height: 24px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            border-radius: 2px;
        }

        .section p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.8;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .highlight {
            color: #667eea;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .stats {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 40px 0;
            padding: 30px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 12px;
        }

        .stat-item {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .stat-number {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #667eea;
            display: block;
        }

        .stat-label {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }

        .cta {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding: 30px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            border-radius: 12px;
            color: white;
        }

        .cta h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .cta p {
            color: white;
            opacity: 0.95;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 14px 32px;
            background: white;
            color: #667eea;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        /* Tablet styles */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                margin: 30px auto;
            }

            .header {
                padding: 40px 30px;
            }

            .header h1 {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
            }

            .header p {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }

            .content {
                padding: 40px 30px;
            }

            .section-title {
                font-size: 1.3rem;
            }

            .section p {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }

            .stats {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
                gap: 15px;
                padding: 20px;
            }

            .stat-number {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
        }

        /* Mobile styles */
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            body {
                padding: 10px;
            }

            .container {
                margin: 20px auto;
                border-radius: 12px;
            }

            .header {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }

            .header h1 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }

            .header p {
                font-size: 0.95rem;
            }

            .content {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }

            .section {
                margin-bottom: 30px;
            }

            .section-title {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }

            .section p {
                font-size: 0.95rem;
                line-height: 1.7;
            }

            .stats {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 20px;
                padding: 20px;
            }

            .stat-number {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
            }

            .cta {
                padding: 25px 20px;
            }

            .cta h3 {
                font-size: 1.3rem;
            }

            .cta-button {
                padding: 12px 28px;
                font-size: 0.95rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Zorin Mobile Shop</h1>
            <p>Your Premier Destination for Quality Products</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="section">
                <h2 class="section-title">Who We Are</h2>
                <p>
                    Welcome to <span class="highlight">Zorin Mobile Shop</span>, your premier destination for seamless
                    online shopping.
                    We are dedicated to providing the best products with a focus on dependability, customer service, and
                    uniqueness.
                    Our commitment to excellence has made us a trusted name in the industry.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="stats">
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <span class="stat-number">2025</span>
                    <span class="stat-label">Founded</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <span class="stat-number">10K+</span>
                    <span class="stat-label">Happy Customers</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <span class="stat-number">100%</span>
                    <span class="stat-label">Satisfaction</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <h2 class="section-title">Our Story</h2>
                <p>
                    Founded in 2025, Zorin Mobile Shop has come a long way from its beginnings. When we first started
                    out,
                    our passion for eco-friendly cleaning products drove us to start our own business. We've grown
                    significantly since then, expanding our product range while maintaining our commitment to
                    sustainability
                    and quality.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <h2 class="section-title">Our Mission</h2>
                <p>
                    We strive to make online shopping an exceptional experience for every customer. Our team works
                    tirelessly to source the finest products, ensure quick delivery, and provide outstanding customer
                    support. Your satisfaction is our top priority, and we're constantly innovating to serve you better.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="cta">
                <h3>Ready to Shop?</h3>
                <p>We hope you enjoy our products as much as we enjoy offering them to you. If you have any questions or
                    comments, please don't hesitate to reach out.</p>
                <a href="#" class="cta-button">Contact Us</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>